# Tistory Skin Coding Rules

- This project is a Tistory skin project.
- Main files are `skin.html`, `style.css`, `index.xml`, and files under `images/`.
- Do not remove Tistory replacement tags unless explicitly requested.
- Prefer simple HTML/CSS/Vanilla JS.
- Do not introduce frameworks such as React, Vue, Tailwind, Bootstrap, or jQuery unless requested.
- Make surgical changes only.
- Avoid unnecessary refactoring.
- Keep layout readable and responsive.
- When modifying multiple files, explain which files changed and why.
- Prioritize maintainability over clever code.